data.enText: a structure on which people, for example criminals, are killed by hanging

data.chText: 把一名男子送上绞刑架
data.enText: to send a man to the gallows (= to send him to his death by hanging)

tr: an instrument of execution consisting of a wooden frame from which a condemned person is executed by hanging

value.def: A gallows is a wooden frame used to execute criminals by hanging.
